				</li>
				<li Class="ScenPart_GameStartDialog">
					<def>GameStartDialog</def>
					<text>The ancient monolith unleashed an energy pulse that tore your research vessel apart and mutated your crew. Only a few of you made it to the escape pods.

Despite the setback, your mission is far from over. If you can learn more about the monolith, perhaps you can find a way to shut it down - or harness its inhuman power.</text>
					<closeSound>GameStartSting</closeSound>
