						<name>Stoned Party</name>
						<adjective>animist</adjective>
						<memberName>Animist</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>Spirit Chief</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Spirit Chief</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>A parallel universe of spirits lies next to our own. A seemingly inanimate object in this universe corresponds to an animated spirit in the other. In the darkness, the spirits are peaceful and satisfied. In the light, they are annoyed and restless. It is said that the spirit of the great &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Drugfinger&lt;/color&gt; will one day grant its wielder power over all spirits.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>A parallel universe of spirits lies next to our own. A seemingly inanimate object in this universe corresponds to an animated spirit in the other. In the darkness, the spirits are peaceful and satisfied. In the light, they are annoyed and restless. It is said that the spirit of the great %%relic0_name%% will one day grant its wielder power over all spirits.</descriptionTemplate>
						<culture>Corunan</culture>
						<iconDef>CirclesE</iconDef>
						<colorDef>DarkRed</colorDef>
						<primaryFactionColor>RGBA(0.865, 0.726, 0.317, 1.000)</primaryFactionColor>
						<memes>
							<li>Structure_Animist</li>
							<li>HighLife</li>
							<li>Darkness</li>
						</memes>
						<precepts>
