						<name>Commune of Archotechnology</name>
						<adjective>archotechnic</adjective>
						<memberName>Archotechnist</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>Archic Chair</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Archic Chair</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>Archotechs are humanity's children and its judges. The archotechs have no interest in judging us one by one. They await a single people who can demonstrate our worthiness by acting morally as one. In the end, the archotechs will depart when they find a people who present themselves as worthy partners to the machine god-consciousness.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>Archotechs are humanity's children and its judges. The archotechs have no interest in judging us one by one. They await a single people who can demonstrate our worthiness by acting morally as one. In the end, the archotechs will depart when they find a people who present themselves as worthy partners to the machine god-consciousness.</descriptionTemplate>
						<culture>Rustican</culture>
						<iconDef>CirclesB</iconDef>
						<colorDef>DarkMauve</colorDef>
						<primaryFactionColor>RGBA(0.447, 0.397, 0.891, 1.000)</primaryFactionColor>
						<memes>
							<li>Structure_Archist</li>
							<li>Collectivist</li>
