						<name>Perfect Legion</name>
						<adjective>Neo-Tantric</adjective>
						<memberName>Neo-Tantran</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>Yogic Chief</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Yogic Chief</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>The universe was a void. Then, &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Agni&lt;/color&gt;, bored with eternity, fashioned man and woman from stone. The faithful fought the unbelievers, and &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Agni&lt;/color&gt; said, "Fight them, everywhere, in my name, until I am worshipped throughout the universe and the true peace may finally reign." Looking upon mankind, &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Agni&lt;/color&gt; found them as children, and declared his dominion over them.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>The universe was a void. Then, %%deity0_name%%, bored with eternity, fashioned man and woman from stone. The faithful fought the unbelievers, and %%deity0_name%% said, "Fight them, everywhere, in my name, until I am worshipped throughout the universe and the true peace may finally reign." Looking upon mankind, %%deity0_name%% found them as children, and declared %%deity0_possessive%% dominion over them.</descriptionTemplate>
						<culture>Corunan</culture>
						<iconDef>Treeflat</iconDef>
						<colorDef>DarkOlive</colorDef>
						<primaryFactionColor>RGBA(0.850, 0.291, 0.291, 1.000)</primaryFactionColor>
						<memes>
							<li>Structure_OriginHindu</li>
							<li>Supremacist</li>
						</memes>
						<precepts>
							<li Class="Precept_Ritual">
								<name>Neo-Tantric Mourning</name>
