						<name>Neo-Animalism</name>
						<adjective>animalistic</adjective>
						<memberName>Animalist</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>Alpha Thug</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Alpha Thug</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>Larry May lived in the forest for twenty years, studying the animals and connecting with them. He came to understand their true morality and founded our movement. May went to commune with the animals in the fields and forests, and connected with them as equals. One day while walking the streets, May was surrounded by filthy beggars. He beat them down, taking the money from the weak and worthless that it might be put to good use.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>Larry May lived in the forest for twenty years, studying the animals and connecting with them. He came to understand their true morality and founded our movement. May went to commune with the animals in the fields and forests, and connected with them as equals. One day while walking the streets, May was surrounded by filthy beggars. He beat them down, taking the money from the weak and worthless that it might be put to good use.</descriptionTemplate>
