						<name>Sanctism</name>
						<adjective>sanctic</adjective>
						<memberName>Sanctic</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>Prime Bishop</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Prime Bishop</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>&lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Onai&lt;/color&gt; wiped away the pollution and machines of the age of smoke to create a garden, wherein she placed the first pure human progenitors. The believers went forth and conquered, burned, and raped for a thousand years, and &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Onai&lt;/color&gt;'s grief at their depravity consumed her. &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Onai&lt;/color&gt; dispersed the great people of Zoutera, sending them into the void so that they may witness the convergence of star and soul.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>%%Deity0_name%% wiped away the pollution and machines of the age of smoke to create a garden, wherein %%deity0_pronoun%% placed the first pure human progenitors. The believers went forth and conquered, burned, and raped for a thousand years, and %%deity0_name%%'s grief at their depravity consumed %%deity0_objective%%. %%Deity0_name%% dispersed the great people of Zoutera, sending them into the void so that they may witness the convergence of star and soul.</descriptionTemplate>
						<culture>Astropolitan</culture>
