						<leaderTitleFemale>Great Captain</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>&lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Hadau&lt;/color&gt; gave birth to humans in a grand accident, and looked upon them with curiosity. Though many adventurers moved against her, &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Hadau&lt;/color&gt; prevented them easily, for she was Spirit of Creation. &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Hadau&lt;/color&gt; dispersed the great people of Novaroma, sending them into the void so that they may witness the convergence of star and soul.</description>
