						<name>Open Path</name>
						<adjective>Neo-Gelugist</adjective>
						<memberName>Neo-Gelugist</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>Wise Sattva</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Wise Sattva</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>One day while working, Taylor 'Duke' Edgell was struck by a great epiphany. He dropped his tools and began spreading his word among the other workers. Duke broke every social rule the oppressors tried to enforce, just to show that he could. None could surpass Duke's understanding of self, and he was appointed the first Wise Sattva of the Neo-Gelugists.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>One day while working, Taylor 'Duke' Edgell was struck by a great epiphany. He dropped his tools and began spreading his word among the other workers. Duke broke every social rule the oppressors tried to enforce, just to show that he could. None could surpass Duke's understanding of self, and he was appointed the first %%leaderTitle%% of the %%memberNamePlural%%.</descriptionTemplate>
